HEADWORD: Stoneroot
<hw>Stone"root`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A North American plant (<spn>Collinsonia Canadensis</spn>) having a
very hard root; horse balm. See <cref>Horse balm</cref>, under
<er>Horse</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

